    "These stages include disease diagnosis, target identification, lead identification, lead optimization, preclinical trials, clinical trials, and drug approval.",
    "For each of these stages, a set of tasks that can benefit from AI is listed.",
    "For an extensive list of such AI tools, please refer to Table 2.",
    "For example, as depicted in Fig. 2 and Table 2, target identification can be enhanced by using ML methods for 3D structure prediction, image reconstruction, and druggability prediction.",
    "Similarly, lead identification can benefit from AI in speeding up virtual screening, pharmacophore modeling, designing synthetic routes, and predicting bioactivity and toxicity."
